EmpathyAI Chatbot
A sentiment-aware chatbot that recognizes emotions and adapts responses to provide support and encouragement.

Setup
Install dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt
Add the emotion_aware folder and the emotion classifier folder into the model folder of the app

Run the application:
python main.py


Features

Detects user emotions in real-time
Provides empathetic support and encouragement
Simple and intuitive user interface
Feedback by clicking the love emoji or the frown

Usage
Start a conversation with EmotiveChat and it will automatically detect your emotions and respond appropriately. 